description:
I've got to take issue with Adrienne on this one.  Lucky 13 has the following qualities that I really like:

(1) Tons of good beers on tap;
(2) Tons of great heavy metal in the jukebox (and some Dick Dale too!);
(3) Tons of free popcorn at happy hour;
(4) A pool table;
(5) A patio;
(6) The least level floor in front of any bar in San Francisco.

Yeah it's grungy, yeah it attracts a certain "hipper than thou" kind of crowd.  So what?  I like it.
